data.description: ***NEW PRICE*** Come check out this STUNNING home in South Fork. You will fall in LOVE with this spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, two story home with an office/den and a bonus room. This home is full of upgrades that you MUST SEE including new SOLAR PANELS. Immediately upon entry, you will see the office/den space featuring French doors. The immaculate kitchen was remodeled in 2022 with custom shaker cabinetry featuring pull out shelving, an extra large island, and beautiful QUARTZ countertops. Just off the kitchen you will find a coffee or wine bar with plenty of space for a few chairs that overlooks the beautifully landscaped back yard. Upstairs you will find the bonus loft with plenty of space, two additional bedrooms with good size closets, full bath, laundry room, and the oversized master suite. This spacious master bathroom includes double sinks, a large stand-up shower, and an oversized walk-in linen closet. The walk-in master closet has been installed with California Closets to maximize the already large space. Through the beautiful French doors in the dining room, you lead into the large screened in lanai featuring 2 ceiling fans. The paver pathway to the secluded 10’x20’ electrified pergola with a custom teak topped bar (including mini fridge), dimmable lighting, and 2 oversized fans is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the sound of the 500 gallon pond-less waterfall feature after a long hard day. This backyard has everything you and your family could ask for! Fully fenced in with access gates on both sides, and low maintenance mature landscaping help to make this an oasis you MUST see! Custom extra large doggy door has been installed for your 4-legged family members to enjoy also! The front and back yard have professionally installed landscape lighting, as well as café lighting to set the mood after dark! Hurricane windows, hurricane shutters, and impact rated doors make this a SAFE home for you and your family as well. NEW A/C system (2022), new hot water heater (2022), the list goes on and on for upgrades, truly a must-see to believe! South Fork has all the amenities you could desire! Multiple dog parks, community pool, basketball courts, and playgrounds. Conveniently located to major highways (with the brand-new onramp to I-75N), stores, dining, and entertainment. Come check it out today before someone snags up your dream home!
